content: I'm planning a trip to Hawaii and I need to pack the right adapters for my devices. Can you help me figure out what kind of power adapters I'll need for my new laptop, Dell XPS 13, and my new smartphone, Samsung Galaxy S22? By the way, I pre-ordered the laptop on January 28th, and it finally arrived on February 25th after a delay from the original expected arrival date of February 11th.
